    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织将提供接近创纪录的 1500 亿美元贷款来应对债务和战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/imf-lending-near-record-150-billion-to-counter-debt-and-wars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织正在向近 100 个国家提供接近创纪录金额的贷款，这证明其在应对大流行后世界的金融和政治危险方面的作用日益增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/imf-lending-near-record-150-billion-to-counter-debt-and-wars</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:43:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>面对 Milei 的乐观情绪，Enel 暂停出售阿根廷 Edesur</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/enel-suspended-sale-of-argentina-s-edesur-amid-milei-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利能源巨头 Enel SpA 发言人表示，该公司周一证实，由于公司高管对总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 放松该行业监管的努力抱有希望，该公司已暂停在阿根廷出售子公司电力分销商 Edesur。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/enel-suspended-sale-of-argentina-s-edesur-amid-milei-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普排除维韦克·拉马斯瓦米作为竞选伙伴，因为他正在寻找新团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-rules-out-ramaswamy-as-running-mate-as-he-eyes-new-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)已经排除了维韦克·拉马斯瓦米(Vivek Ramaswamy)作为他的竞选搭档，转而关注这位企业家担任内阁职务，这位共和党总统候选人正在评估可能的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-rules-out-ramaswamy-as-running-mate-as-he-eyes-new-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登拒绝出席本周的公共众议院听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/hunter-biden-refuses-to-appear-at-public-house-hearing-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登拒绝了在国会公开听证会上作证的邀请，该听证会涉及商业活动，而商业活动是共和党对其父亲、总统乔·拜登弹劾调查的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/hunter-biden-refuses-to-appear-at-public-house-hearing-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俱乐部谈判陷入僵局后英国将制定足球监管法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/uk-to-set-out-football-regulation-law-after-club-talks-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将立法设立独立的足球监管机构，在顶级英超联赛和低级别英格兰足球联赛之间重新分配收入，政府将进行干预，努力保障小型俱乐部的财务可持续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/uk-to-set-out-football-regulation-law-after-club-talks-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果工党赢得权力，里夫斯将支持英国财政部的增长部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/reeves-to-bolster-uk-treasury-s-growth-unit-if-labour-wins-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯(Rachel Reeves)周二向伦敦金融城银行家阐述了工党政府的经济愿景，她将承诺改革英国财政部，将经济增长“硬连接”到其财政规划中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/reeves-to-bolster-uk-treasury-s-growth-unit-if-labour-wins-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议员们拒绝上议院修正案，苏纳克的卢旺达法案取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sunak-s-rwanda-bill-progresses-as-mps-reject-lords-amendments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国立法者拒绝了上议院对其将寻求庇护者驱逐到卢旺达的计划提出的一系列修改建议，从而使首相里希·苏纳克能够在履行其主要移民承诺方面取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sunak-s-rwanda-bill-progresses-as-mps-reject-lords-amendments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:24:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普挑战让地方检察官威利斯继续审理佐治亚州案件的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-challenges-ruling-letting-da-willis-stay-on-georgia-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和七名共同被告希望获得许可，对佐治亚州法官的裁决提出上诉，该裁决规定富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯可以继续参与备受关注的州选举干扰案，尽管她与一名高级检察官有恋情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-challenges-ruling-letting-da-willis-stay-on-georgia-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 20:00:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储在 6 月降息的可能性不到 50% 的情况下进行价格互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fed-swaps-price-in-less-than-50-chance-of-a-june-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高盛集团的掉期交易员和经济学家预测美联储降息幅度较小，两年期和五年期国债收益率攀升至今年最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fed-swaps-price-in-less-than-50-chance-of-a-june-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 16:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
